WEBVTT

00:00:30.855 --> 00:00:32.813
Old guard, what are you doing?

00:00:33.438 --> 00:00:35.271
Lotus roots can heal his wounds.

00:00:35.355 --> 00:00:38.480
The Third Crown Prince
dismembered himself to repay his parents.

00:00:38.563 --> 00:00:42.188
Then his master used lotus stems and roots
to regrow his flesh and bones.

00:00:42.271 --> 00:00:44.271
How many milk caps did he use this time?

00:00:44.355 --> 00:00:46.563
No idea.
Everything was on fire when I arrived.

00:00:46.646 --> 00:00:50.396
The Nine Dragons Divine Fire Barrier
has the worst side effects.

00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:51.771
When will he come to?

00:00:51.855 --> 00:00:54.105
Don't worry. He won't die.

00:01:19.521 --> 00:01:23.146
AGENT FROM ABOVE

00:01:23.646 --> 00:01:27.938
INTO THE ABYSS

00:01:45.396 --> 00:01:46.688
Baby, don't go.

00:01:58.271 --> 00:01:59.105
Han Chieh.

00:02:00.188 --> 00:02:01.355
You're awake?

00:02:01.855 --> 00:02:03.646
How do you feel now?

00:02:18.521 --> 00:02:20.896
Sure you want to take on
so many cases at once?

00:02:21.605 --> 00:02:23.438
Screw it, I'm going all in.

00:02:23.521 --> 00:02:25.105
Han Chieh, what are you doing?

00:02:26.605 --> 00:02:28.855
DEMON KING ENTICES MAN

00:02:28.938 --> 00:02:31.105
But you said the Demon King
has a new agent.

00:02:31.188 --> 00:02:34.105
-You don't know anything about him.
-I don't give a fuck.

00:02:34.688 --> 00:02:37.771
If I don't stop that scumbag,
more innocent people will die.

00:02:38.271 --> 00:02:39.813
CHIEH

00:02:42.146 --> 00:02:43.355
Happy now?

00:02:43.938 --> 00:02:44.896
Hey.

00:02:45.730 --> 00:02:46.730
Hey!

00:02:57.355 --> 00:03:01.230
"Go to Buddha Mountain
for a healthy hike."

00:03:03.521 --> 00:03:04.980
Buddha Mountain?

00:03:07.563 --> 00:03:08.771
Chen Chi-sha.

00:03:10.771 --> 00:03:11.605
Fuck.

00:03:11.688 --> 00:03:12.688
BUDDHA

00:03:12.771 --> 00:03:14.480
After I defeated Chen Chi-sha,

00:03:14.563 --> 00:03:18.063
I locked all his magical weapons
in a safe.

00:03:35.271 --> 00:03:36.521
Stop practicing sorcery.

00:03:37.188 --> 00:03:38.313
Retire.

00:03:39.230 --> 00:03:41.563
I'll protect you
from any demons or ghosts.

00:03:43.771 --> 00:03:45.980
Do you really think you're invincible?

00:03:56.146 --> 00:03:57.855
You got lucky this time.

00:03:59.021 --> 00:04:01.271
If the Demon King regains his full power,

00:04:01.980 --> 00:04:02.938
you're dead meat.

00:04:09.813 --> 00:04:13.730
Doesn't sound like
there's anything good in this safe.

00:04:13.813 --> 00:04:15.563
Sure he isn't messing with you?

00:04:15.646 --> 00:04:17.646
He sent me that message for a reason.

00:04:17.730 --> 00:04:20.021
He wouldn't mess with me
just for the sake of it.

00:04:20.730 --> 00:04:24.521
Fuck, I think you're messing with me.
How much farther is it?

00:04:29.146 --> 00:04:30.188
Hey.

00:04:31.980 --> 00:04:33.063
Have you got the key?

00:04:52.813 --> 00:04:54.063
What the fuck.

00:04:55.646 --> 00:04:58.855
ZERO, ONE, TWO, THREE,
FOUR, FIVE, SIX, SEVEN, EIGHT, NINE

00:04:58.938 --> 00:05:00.855
What the fuck is that?

00:05:54.605 --> 00:05:55.938
What the…

00:06:00.771 --> 00:06:01.896
Mother of…

00:06:03.938 --> 00:06:04.813
What's that?

00:06:16.646 --> 00:06:18.105
Come on… let's go.

00:06:19.230 --> 00:06:20.355
Go.

00:06:24.730 --> 00:06:25.563
Incense ash.

00:06:40.146 --> 00:06:42.230
Did Chen Chi-sha put you in that safe?

00:06:44.730 --> 00:06:45.855
Why?

00:06:51.896 --> 00:06:52.980
Me?

00:06:54.438 --> 00:06:55.938
He wants to tell me something?

00:06:57.730 --> 00:06:58.563
Wu…

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:00.646
Wu Tien-chi?

00:07:04.021 --> 00:07:07.021
Wu Meng-hsueh.

00:07:10.021 --> 00:07:11.605
Wu Meng-hsueh?

00:07:15.521 --> 00:07:16.855
Look up Wu Meng-hsueh.

00:07:17.938 --> 00:07:20.605
-I'll do a search back at the station.
-Okay.

00:07:23.688 --> 00:07:24.938
On the left…

00:07:27.146 --> 00:07:28.438
Hide…

00:07:29.646 --> 00:07:31.271
Cut it out, cut it out…

00:07:31.355 --> 00:07:33.896
Cut it out-- Go…

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.855
-Okay, go.
-Wang Hsiao-ming.

00:07:35.938 --> 00:07:36.813
Yes.

00:07:36.980 --> 00:07:38.396
Who pays for the internet?

00:07:39.521 --> 00:07:41.063
Watch out. Grenade!

00:07:41.146 --> 00:07:42.271
You do.

00:07:42.355 --> 00:07:43.646
Fire in the hole!

00:07:43.730 --> 00:07:46.313
Be a big brother
and look after the little ghost.

00:07:47.021 --> 00:07:48.313
-What?
-What?

00:07:48.396 --> 00:07:50.855
Okay… sure.

00:07:52.646 --> 00:07:54.313
-I'm off.
-Bye.

00:07:59.730 --> 00:08:00.771
Let's play.

00:08:06.938 --> 00:08:07.855
What do you want?

00:08:08.355 --> 00:08:09.855
I need to pee.

00:08:12.605 --> 00:08:14.188
I need to pee.

00:08:15.230 --> 00:08:17.063
Fuck, he needs to pee. What do I do?

00:08:17.896 --> 00:08:18.813
Hey!

00:08:19.730 --> 00:08:20.563
CRIMINAL FILE

00:08:20.646 --> 00:08:24.021
Wu Meng-hsueh changed his name
to Wu Tien-chi. He's in finance now.

00:08:24.105 --> 00:08:27.146
Rumor has it
he can predict the stock market

00:08:27.230 --> 00:08:28.938
and how shares will perform.

00:08:29.730 --> 00:08:31.605
He even committed murder as a minor.

00:08:36.146 --> 00:08:38.271
Chen Chi-sha said Wu's the new agent.

00:08:39.021 --> 00:08:40.896
That they were just using him.

00:08:40.980 --> 00:08:45.230
Now Chen Chi-sha is dead,
Wu Tien-chi probably has Wang Yu-ching.

00:08:47.313 --> 00:08:48.146
What for?

00:08:55.105 --> 00:08:56.063
Mr. Wang.

00:09:02.813 --> 00:09:06.188
You'll wear yourself out like this.
Go home and get some rest.

00:09:06.271 --> 00:09:09.146
We'll inform you
the second we get any news.

00:09:10.063 --> 00:09:13.188
I'm fine. I'll wait here for Ching.

00:09:13.938 --> 00:09:16.063
There's no one else back home anyway.

00:09:32.188 --> 00:09:33.105
Hello?

00:09:34.021 --> 00:09:35.688
Is this Yu-ching's dad?

00:09:36.438 --> 00:09:37.605
Yes, it is.

00:09:38.230 --> 00:09:39.063
I'm her friend.

00:09:39.813 --> 00:09:43.396
Have you heard
how she's being bullied at school?

00:09:43.480 --> 00:09:47.813
She's being bullied at school?
She never mentioned it before.

00:09:48.313 --> 00:09:49.521
Are you her classmate?

00:09:49.605 --> 00:09:52.605
I know where to find her,
but I don't want to get in trouble.

00:09:53.188 --> 00:09:56.855
So you must promise me
not to call the cops.

00:09:57.563 --> 00:10:01.021
-That's the only way I can help.
-Okay, I promise.

00:10:04.730 --> 00:10:05.605
CRIMINAL FILES

00:10:05.688 --> 00:10:08.563
I handled Wu Meng-hsueh's case back then.

00:10:09.313 --> 00:10:10.355
Some 20 years ago.

00:10:10.438 --> 00:10:12.813
You still remember the case,
Prosecutor Chen?

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:14.813
I'll never forget it.

00:10:15.688 --> 00:10:18.521
I was outraged by the verdict.

00:10:18.605 --> 00:10:21.813
PRESIDING JUDGE: CHANG HO-CHENG

00:10:28.980 --> 00:10:29.813
What is it?

00:10:32.230 --> 00:10:33.230
Please continue.

00:10:33.813 --> 00:10:35.396
Wu Meng-hsueh was 15.

00:10:36.188 --> 00:10:39.230
The victim was a 16-year-old girl.

00:10:40.063 --> 00:10:42.771
She and her grandma
were found dead in their own home.

00:10:43.605 --> 00:10:45.896
-What was the motive?
-A crime of passion.

00:10:45.980 --> 00:10:48.021
The girl had been sexually assaulted.

00:10:48.105 --> 00:10:51.730
He claimed they were in love,
but the grandma opposed the relationship.

00:10:52.438 --> 00:10:55.355
Wu Meng-hsueh's dad was a famous lawyer.

00:10:55.438 --> 00:10:57.855
He assembled a big legal team
to to exonerate him.

00:10:57.938 --> 00:11:00.980
They used his status as a minor
to exploit legal loopholes.

00:11:02.230 --> 00:11:06.188
The victim's grandpa was always in court,
but couldn't speak because of a stroke.

00:11:07.230 --> 00:11:11.146
His dad also used his connections
to put pressure on the presiding judge.

00:11:11.730 --> 00:11:16.480
He got off with a light sentence
and there was nothing I could do about it.

00:11:17.605 --> 00:11:21.105
The girl's grandpa
refused to eat or drink after the verdict.

00:11:21.188 --> 00:11:22.771
He died not long after.

00:11:23.271 --> 00:11:26.105
Wu Meng-hsueh
didn't stay inside for long either.

00:11:26.688 --> 00:11:29.855
He was released in his twenties
and regained his freedom.

00:11:32.105 --> 00:11:35.063
I'm angry at myself
for failing to get justice for her.

00:11:35.771 --> 00:11:37.563
But I'm even angrier at this world.

00:11:38.146 --> 00:11:40.813
Those with power and influence
get away with anything.

00:11:47.771 --> 00:11:50.980
PRESIDING JUDGE, CHANG HO-CHENG

00:11:57.480 --> 00:12:00.021
I asked his dad's secretary
to meet me nearby.

00:12:03.896 --> 00:12:06.563
You've been acting weird.
What's the matter?

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:13.730
Wu Meng-hsueh's presiding judge,
Chang Ho-cheng, was my dad.

00:12:17.313 --> 00:12:19.938
He didn't talk to us about work often.

00:12:20.438 --> 00:12:23.271
When I was in high school,
he suddenly became depressed.

00:12:23.355 --> 00:12:25.480
He died not long after that.

00:12:26.063 --> 00:12:29.438
In the days before he died,
he kept saying, "I'm sorry."

00:12:29.521 --> 00:12:31.563
I finally found out why today.

00:12:32.813 --> 00:12:36.313
He couldn't get over the verdict.
It haunted him to his death.

00:12:38.563 --> 00:12:42.230
Even gods make mistakes,
what hope do humans have?

00:12:45.563 --> 00:12:48.438
Fuck. I swear to god
I'll throw that asshole in jail.

00:12:50.105 --> 00:12:50.980
Jail?

00:12:51.605 --> 00:12:54.730
Men like him should go straight
to the 18th level of hell.

00:12:57.063 --> 00:12:58.146
The 100th level.

00:13:03.355 --> 00:13:06.563
Secretary Liu, I'm Chang Min.
We spoke on the phone.

00:13:06.646 --> 00:13:07.980
This is my partner.

00:13:08.563 --> 00:13:13.521
Today, I came to ask you about
Mr. Wu's son, Wu Meng-hsueh.

00:13:23.313 --> 00:13:24.438
Secretary Liu.

00:13:32.355 --> 00:13:34.021
What do you want to know?

00:13:34.105 --> 00:13:36.938
After Wu Meng-hsueh was released,
he got a new identity.

00:13:37.021 --> 00:13:39.438
Is there anything
he was hiding from or avoiding?

00:13:39.521 --> 00:13:43.438
His family was already powerful.
Why did he learn the Wumeng Technique?

00:13:46.355 --> 00:13:47.230
Because…

00:13:49.188 --> 00:13:51.105
he saw that girl's grandpa in jail.

00:13:54.063 --> 00:13:55.063
Go away.

00:13:55.146 --> 00:13:56.188
Get lost.

00:13:57.605 --> 00:14:00.230
You killed my wife and granddaughter.

00:14:00.771 --> 00:14:03.105
I'll haunt you until the day you die.

00:14:03.188 --> 00:14:06.188
I'll settle this score with you
in the Underworld!

00:14:08.688 --> 00:14:10.396
I'll personally see you go down

00:14:10.480 --> 00:14:12.271
to the 18th level of hell!

00:14:13.438 --> 00:14:17.271
Wu Meng-hsueh asked his dad for help,
so Mr. Wu found a master

00:14:17.355 --> 00:14:21.271
who kept the grandpa's spirit
in a sandalwood incense burner,

00:14:21.355 --> 00:14:23.521
and sealed it inside with talismans.

00:14:25.313 --> 00:14:27.105
Do you know where it is now?

00:14:29.063 --> 00:14:30.105
No, I don't.

00:14:31.021 --> 00:14:33.105
I just know
that after Wu Meng-hsueh got out,

00:14:33.188 --> 00:14:34.730
he traveled the world.

00:14:36.646 --> 00:14:38.188
His goal was to find a way

00:14:38.938 --> 00:14:42.938
to act with impunity, free from punishment
in both the Human Realm and hell.

00:14:43.771 --> 00:14:46.105
He started studying
black magic and sorcery,

00:14:46.188 --> 00:14:49.313
including the worst magic of all,
the Wumeng Technique.

00:14:52.438 --> 00:14:53.855
What have you done?

00:14:55.355 --> 00:14:59.605
We had four competitors. All of which
had staff members involved in accidents.

00:14:59.688 --> 00:15:02.855
But we're in a great position now.
What are you unhappy about?

00:15:02.938 --> 00:15:04.063
Meng-hsueh.

00:15:04.813 --> 00:15:07.355
Stop engaging in these shady practices.

00:15:09.063 --> 00:15:10.313
If you keep this up…

00:15:12.896 --> 00:15:14.021
I'll change my will.

00:15:15.355 --> 00:15:17.896
When the time comes,
you won't get a single penny.

00:15:21.021 --> 00:15:22.271
Try me.

00:15:25.105 --> 00:15:26.771
If you change your will,

00:15:27.480 --> 00:15:29.146
the next one to have an accident

00:15:30.021 --> 00:15:31.355
might well be you.

00:15:31.980 --> 00:15:32.855
You…

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:35.980
I should've let them
throw the book at you!

00:15:45.855 --> 00:15:48.146
Later, Mr. Wu closed the law firm.

00:15:49.980 --> 00:15:52.021
And I left my job after he retired.

00:15:52.813 --> 00:15:54.980
I never heard from them again.

00:16:05.521 --> 00:16:07.063
Let's find that incense burner.

00:16:08.063 --> 00:16:09.063
Why?

00:16:10.438 --> 00:16:12.438
The only thing he fears is karma.

00:16:13.188 --> 00:16:14.896
Being reported to the Underworld.

00:16:15.938 --> 00:16:19.355
You mean that if the girl's grandpa
reports him to Yama,

00:16:19.855 --> 00:16:23.063
he'll have to face up
to all his crimes when he dies?

00:16:23.688 --> 00:16:26.438
Yeah. Can you find where it's hidden?

00:16:27.646 --> 00:16:29.896
I asked the station to pull his records.

00:16:29.980 --> 00:16:31.313
He has a foreign passport.

00:16:31.396 --> 00:16:34.105
His assets are all held overseas.
It'll take some time.

00:16:36.188 --> 00:16:40.605
The Demon King sure knows how to pick
them. This guy's cunning and has brains.

00:16:41.188 --> 00:16:43.855
So what if he has brains?
He only uses them for evil.

00:16:43.938 --> 00:16:45.896
You're brainless, but better than him.

00:16:46.396 --> 00:16:48.063
You're the fucking brainless one.

00:16:48.146 --> 00:16:49.396
Touchy.

00:16:51.605 --> 00:16:53.980
INVESTIGATION UNIT ONE

00:16:54.063 --> 00:16:55.771
-Damn it, you bastard!
-Calm down.

00:16:55.855 --> 00:16:57.271
Where's my daughter?

00:16:57.771 --> 00:16:58.938
Where's my daughter?

00:17:03.480 --> 00:17:04.313
Good job.

00:17:06.730 --> 00:17:09.563
The beat-up guy is a drug user
called Hsieh Kun-hao.

00:17:09.646 --> 00:17:13.021
A man phoned Wang Cheng-nan saying
Mr. Hsieh was bullying his daughter.

00:17:13.105 --> 00:17:15.771
So he assumed
he must be the one who kidnapped her.

00:17:16.396 --> 00:17:17.521
How did he find him?

00:17:17.605 --> 00:17:19.396
The man on the phone told him.

00:17:19.480 --> 00:17:22.855
He found him at an apartment
Wu Tien-chi bought three years ago.

00:17:22.938 --> 00:17:24.855
The same place the girl and grandma died.

00:17:27.938 --> 00:17:30.313
Using others
while keeping safely out of it.

00:17:31.313 --> 00:17:32.355
Seems to be his MO.

00:17:33.480 --> 00:17:35.563
Chao already invited him over for a chat.

00:17:38.230 --> 00:17:40.855
I bought that apartment ages ago

00:17:40.938 --> 00:17:42.563
and it's been empty for years.

00:17:43.938 --> 00:17:46.105
God knows why anyone would break in.

00:17:46.688 --> 00:17:48.313
So why did you buy the property?

00:17:53.813 --> 00:17:57.146
It's in a good location
and bound to gain value in the future.

00:17:57.813 --> 00:18:00.021
I only bought it for investment purposes.

00:18:04.438 --> 00:18:07.396
Officers, is there anything else
you'd like to ask?

00:18:13.730 --> 00:18:15.188
-Thank you.
-Take care.

00:18:18.480 --> 00:18:22.146
-You're just letting him go?
-We can't detain him.

00:18:22.230 --> 00:18:26.188
We have no evidence connecting him
to the girl's disappearance.

00:18:26.271 --> 00:18:28.521
And the number used to call Wang Cheng-nan

00:18:28.605 --> 00:18:30.521
wasn't even a Taiwanese number.

00:18:30.605 --> 00:18:33.771
So we can't be sure he made the call.

00:18:34.271 --> 00:18:35.396
But…

00:18:35.480 --> 00:18:37.605
All right, have him tailed 24-7.

00:18:39.271 --> 00:18:40.188
Got it.

00:18:49.063 --> 00:18:50.105
Hello.

00:18:51.563 --> 00:18:52.688
Cut the act.

00:18:54.688 --> 00:18:55.563
Oh.

00:19:06.313 --> 00:19:07.688
I'm impressed.

00:19:08.438 --> 00:19:11.730
You went to see Chen Chi-sha
and actually got out alive.

00:19:14.230 --> 00:19:17.771
Tell the Demon King
I know he's coming up here for me.

00:19:17.855 --> 00:19:21.771
I'm happy to play along,
but you must release Wang Yu-ching first.

00:19:22.355 --> 00:19:25.521
And let's set some rules.
Leave innocent people out of this.

00:19:26.980 --> 00:19:30.396
You love messing with black magic, right?
Then let's fight.

00:19:30.480 --> 00:19:33.896
If you win, you can take my life.

00:19:41.605 --> 00:19:43.230
That sounds pretty tempting.

00:19:44.605 --> 00:19:48.021
Shame you don't know me so well.
Let me tell you something.

00:19:48.105 --> 00:19:52.188
There's nothing I hate more
than obeying stupid rules.

00:19:53.855 --> 00:19:55.480
See those people in there?

00:19:56.146 --> 00:19:59.855
They bow and scrape,
always following the rules,

00:20:01.021 --> 00:20:03.230
and live out lives of drudgery.

00:20:03.938 --> 00:20:05.188
In search of what?

00:20:05.771 --> 00:20:06.896
Freedom.

00:20:07.896 --> 00:20:10.105
Nothing beats freedom.

00:20:15.730 --> 00:20:17.521
I hear your milk caps are pretty fancy.

00:20:20.646 --> 00:20:22.313
Can't wait to see for myself.

00:20:42.605 --> 00:20:43.563
Hello.

00:20:44.938 --> 00:20:46.063
This way, please.

00:20:46.688 --> 00:20:48.855
The VIP has arrived.

00:21:16.313 --> 00:21:18.730
It's getting cold.
Add an extra blanket at night.

00:21:18.813 --> 00:21:20.271
I know, I'm not five.

00:21:20.355 --> 00:21:22.646
You'll be reminding me
to wear socks to bed next.

00:21:23.646 --> 00:21:25.021
-Bye.
-Bye.

00:21:54.063 --> 00:21:55.355
What are you back for?

00:22:00.480 --> 00:22:01.396
Leafy.

00:22:02.730 --> 00:22:04.063
Leafy.

00:22:05.563 --> 00:22:06.480
Leafy.

00:22:21.271 --> 00:22:22.146
Go on, jump.

00:22:23.146 --> 00:22:24.271
Jump.

00:22:25.188 --> 00:22:26.021
Jump.

00:22:26.521 --> 00:22:27.730
Hurry up and jump.

00:22:27.813 --> 00:22:28.855
Jump.

00:22:28.938 --> 00:22:31.313
You bastard! Stay away from her!

00:22:52.480 --> 00:22:53.355
Leafy.

00:22:54.146 --> 00:22:54.980
Leafy.

00:22:59.480 --> 00:23:00.521
Chieh.

00:23:56.688 --> 00:23:57.855
What do you want?

00:23:58.438 --> 00:23:59.730
Wait…

00:24:01.813 --> 00:24:06.105
I just sent my cute secretary
to case the joint and check things out.

00:24:06.688 --> 00:24:08.521
I feel bad for Master Chen.

00:24:08.605 --> 00:24:12.271
I wanted to find him a goddaughter.
Maybe Yeh Chih-ling?

00:24:14.230 --> 00:24:16.605
You dare touch my people?
I'll end you right now!

00:24:20.980 --> 00:24:22.896
You've never killed a human, have you?

00:24:25.480 --> 00:24:29.521
Lots of demons and ghosts,
but never a living human being?

00:24:30.146 --> 00:24:31.438
Want to give it a go?

00:24:33.021 --> 00:24:34.646
You want to kill me, right?

00:24:35.105 --> 00:24:37.313
See. We're the same.

00:24:38.105 --> 00:24:39.230
We're the same.

00:24:39.313 --> 00:24:41.521
-Chieh…
-We're the same.

00:24:41.605 --> 00:24:42.980
-Calm down, Chieh.
-Come on.

00:24:43.063 --> 00:24:44.230
Chieh.

00:24:45.355 --> 00:24:48.521
Fuck, you've got some mouth on you,
but all you do is talk.

00:24:48.605 --> 00:24:52.688
All talk and no action. Relying on
Chen Chi-sha to do all your dirty work.

00:24:58.063 --> 00:25:00.896
Officer, who do you think you are?

00:25:00.980 --> 00:25:05.105
You think your corrupt, incompetent unit
has what it takes to arrest me?

00:25:05.605 --> 00:25:06.938
Maybe in your next life.

00:25:07.438 --> 00:25:09.980
That it? Is that all you've got?

00:25:10.563 --> 00:25:12.313
Guess that's your idea of an insult?

00:25:12.396 --> 00:25:15.021
Why'd the Demon King
choose a loser like you?

00:25:15.646 --> 00:25:17.188
Try harder, will you?

00:25:22.563 --> 00:25:24.521
Chen Chi-sha was just a pawn.

00:25:24.605 --> 00:25:27.896
I told him who to kill.

00:25:27.980 --> 00:25:30.605
That old fart
isn't even on the same level, okay?

00:25:30.688 --> 00:25:32.021
You're a bunch of losers.

00:25:32.105 --> 00:25:35.980
I know the law. I know black magic.
Think you're a match for me?

00:25:36.063 --> 00:25:38.063
I might just kill Yeh Chih-ling first.

00:25:39.146 --> 00:25:40.855
Chieh, let's go.

00:25:40.938 --> 00:25:42.980
Chieh. Come on, let's go.

00:25:43.980 --> 00:25:45.480
What? Don't go!

00:25:53.563 --> 00:25:57.105
There, there now. Calm down.
It's okay. I'll open the door for you.

00:25:58.021 --> 00:26:00.396
Get in the car. Watch your head.

00:26:00.480 --> 00:26:02.271
Sit properly and be good.

00:26:05.396 --> 00:26:07.813
Low blood sugar makes you irritable.

00:26:27.438 --> 00:26:28.313
Chao.

00:26:28.896 --> 00:26:33.980
Listen, thanks to Han Chieh,
we can file for a search warrant.

00:26:36.605 --> 00:26:37.896
I'll send it over later.

00:26:44.313 --> 00:26:45.480
What's so funny?

00:26:50.521 --> 00:26:52.896
Chen Chi-sha was just a pawn.

00:26:52.980 --> 00:26:56.396
I told him who to kill.

00:26:56.480 --> 00:26:57.480
That old fart--

00:27:04.605 --> 00:27:07.730
Prosecutor Chen approved
a search warrant for Wu Tien-chi's home.

00:27:07.813 --> 00:27:09.188
Beside the recording,

00:27:09.271 --> 00:27:13.230
he was also seen entering a private room
with Chen Chi-sha at the nightclub.

00:27:28.313 --> 00:27:32.271
This sandalwood incense burner
with talismans on it was kept well hidden.

00:27:32.355 --> 00:27:34.146
Is this what you're looking for?

00:27:39.646 --> 00:27:40.480
Yes.

00:27:40.980 --> 00:27:43.230
Chieh, that's evidence.

00:27:43.730 --> 00:27:45.938
Remember to return it after you're done.

00:27:54.188 --> 00:27:56.855
So what are you planning to do with it?

00:27:58.855 --> 00:27:59.980
I'll hold onto it

00:28:00.063 --> 00:28:03.063
and help the girl's grandpa
request a Black Command Token.

00:28:06.688 --> 00:28:08.938
We finally got something on him.

00:28:09.021 --> 00:28:10.688
Screw that Wu Tien-chi.

00:28:19.396 --> 00:28:21.271
TAIPEI CITY STREET MAP

00:28:24.271 --> 00:28:25.855
Hey, I don't get it.

00:28:25.938 --> 00:28:29.063
Wu Tien-chi tricked Wang Cheng-nan
into going after that other guy.

00:28:29.146 --> 00:28:32.105
He even chose the apartment
where he committed his first murder

00:28:32.188 --> 00:28:33.563
as the location.

00:28:33.646 --> 00:28:34.646
What's he up to?

00:28:36.063 --> 00:28:39.771
The location… of his first murder.

00:28:41.980 --> 00:28:43.271
Wu Tien-chi's objective…

00:28:44.605 --> 00:28:45.896
That girl isn't here.

00:28:45.980 --> 00:28:48.771
Wang Yu-ching has other uses.

00:28:50.188 --> 00:28:51.563
Wu Tien-chi's apartment.

00:28:52.605 --> 00:28:53.438
Heilung HQ.

00:28:54.688 --> 00:28:56.146
Those stolen primal souls.

00:28:56.230 --> 00:28:58.396
PAOAN TEMPLE, LANTE TEMPLE, FUHE TEMPLE

00:28:58.480 --> 00:29:01.438
The deaths at each location
happened in the same weird way.

00:29:06.855 --> 00:29:08.646
Give me a pen…

00:29:16.021 --> 00:29:17.480
HEILUNG HQ

00:29:22.980 --> 00:29:23.813
FUHE TEMPLE

00:29:23.896 --> 00:29:25.063
LANCHEN TEMPLE

00:29:25.855 --> 00:29:26.688
PAOAN TEMPLE

00:29:30.521 --> 00:29:31.771
This is…

00:29:32.271 --> 00:29:33.396
It's an array.

00:29:43.521 --> 00:29:44.938
Fuck.

00:29:46.146 --> 00:29:47.271
I missed it.

00:29:47.771 --> 00:29:49.730
While Chen Chi-sha grabbed primal souls,

00:29:49.813 --> 00:29:51.813
Wu set up the array
with live sacrifices.

00:29:52.396 --> 00:29:55.813
He'll break the seal and help
the Demon King enter the Human Realm.

00:30:02.813 --> 00:30:04.688
"Corpselords will rise

00:30:04.771 --> 00:30:06.521
and attack at full moon."

00:30:06.605 --> 00:30:07.521
The full moon?

00:30:09.771 --> 00:30:11.688
It was a full moon last time too.

00:30:17.438 --> 00:30:18.563
You got lucky.

00:30:19.480 --> 00:30:22.188
If the Demon King
regains his full power, you're dead meat.

00:30:23.271 --> 00:30:25.896
Full moon, magic array, center.

00:30:27.021 --> 00:30:30.230
I get it now.
Five years ago, I only managed to win

00:30:30.896 --> 00:30:33.730
because I stopped
the Demon King's entry just in time.

00:30:34.688 --> 00:30:37.313
The magic array was complete,
but he was waiting

00:30:37.396 --> 00:30:40.355
for midnight
when the moon is at its height.

00:30:40.438 --> 00:30:43.563
Only then could he regain his full power
through the portal.

00:30:44.230 --> 00:30:48.146
If you dare get in my way,
I'll drag you down to hell with me.

00:30:48.771 --> 00:30:49.980
It's the same this time.

00:30:52.188 --> 00:30:53.688
WANG YU-CHING, HEILUNG HQ

00:30:54.271 --> 00:30:55.146
Where's the portal?

00:30:57.980 --> 00:30:59.896
At the center of the array,

00:31:01.063 --> 00:31:02.230
Dongfeng Market.

00:31:06.021 --> 00:31:09.063
So he targeted you and Dongfeng Market
right from the start.

00:31:09.563 --> 00:31:11.146
That bastard, Wu Tien-chi.

00:31:17.063 --> 00:31:18.646
But the array is incomplete.

00:31:19.813 --> 00:31:23.896
The sacrifice at the final location
must be Wang Yu-ching.

00:31:23.980 --> 00:31:25.730
GOLDEN LAKE PLAZA

00:31:26.313 --> 00:31:27.938
Can't we just survey the place?

00:31:28.021 --> 00:31:30.938
It's surrounded by high-rises
with thousands of households.

00:31:31.021 --> 00:31:32.146
He could be anywhere.

00:31:38.730 --> 00:31:42.688
A human is sacrificed
either by suicide or brutal murder.

00:31:43.271 --> 00:31:47.688
The array's dark power is fueled by the
victims' terror and resentment in death.

00:31:50.063 --> 00:31:53.438
He's keeping Wang Yu-ching alive
for the final sacrifice

00:31:53.521 --> 00:31:56.396
a few days before the full moon.

00:31:57.105 --> 00:31:58.313
We still have time.

00:32:01.730 --> 00:32:05.605
GOLDEN LAKE PLAZA

00:33:15.396 --> 00:33:18.146
-Do we still have a deal?
-You're pathetic.

00:33:18.230 --> 00:33:21.813
Are you that scared of an old man
filing a complaint against you?

00:33:22.813 --> 00:33:25.021
Just do this right,

00:33:25.105 --> 00:33:28.188
and even Yama of the Underworld
won't be able to touch you,

00:33:28.271 --> 00:33:31.980
no matter what you did in the Human Realm

00:33:32.063 --> 00:33:35.438
and even if you die and end up in hell.

00:33:36.980 --> 00:33:41.105
Do you have what I asked for?
How are preparations going?

00:33:42.355 --> 00:33:43.646
It's all set.

00:33:46.146 --> 00:33:47.646
I tried it out today.

00:33:49.271 --> 00:33:52.521
Chieh, Leafy has been possessed
by a female ghost.

00:33:53.563 --> 00:33:54.563
What do you want?

00:33:55.063 --> 00:33:57.146
That little shit really cares about her.

00:34:00.771 --> 00:34:03.146
If we put it in that girl,

00:34:03.230 --> 00:34:04.980
even if Han Chieh finds out,

00:34:05.063 --> 00:34:07.063
he won't dare do anything rash.

00:34:14.313 --> 00:34:17.396
Don't underestimate him.

00:34:17.480 --> 00:34:20.771
He defeated Chen Chi-sha.

00:34:21.271 --> 00:34:23.521
You'd better mind yourself.

00:34:24.396 --> 00:34:26.480
This is the final stretch.

00:34:26.980 --> 00:34:28.938
Raise the corpselords first.

00:34:29.021 --> 00:34:32.771
Find a way to exhaust his magic weapons.